headline: Hormel Foods Corporation (HRL) Announced 388th Consecutive Quarterly Dividend
summary: On May 19, Hormel Foods Corporation (NYSE:HRL) declared a quarterly dividend of $0.29 per share, which was consistent with its previous dividend. The Minnesota-based multinational food processing company specializes in the production and distribution of branded meat and food products, offering a range of processed meats, poultry items, and prepared foods. headline: Hormel Foods Corporation Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: Hormel Foods Corporation (NYSE: HRL), a Fortune 500 global branded food company, today announced its quarterly dividend on the common stock, authorized by the Board of Directors at 29.00 cents ($0.29) a share on May 19, 2025, will be paid August 15, 2025, to stockholders of record at the close of business on July 14, 2025.
